        "timestamp": "2018-08-14 13:44:52.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\nAs far as I know, these properties are not a mistake. There are different objects created at different times by different components, then attached to each other. Once attached, they could be queried and traversed as a graph, but before then, they need their own attributes to be joined together.\n\nI will ask the dev team if it can be optimised.",
